I would love to see a classic server with none of the expansions.  Of course not many would want to play it, but I guess I just miss the old days of playing EQ when the game was fun and a little more simple.  When getting a full set of banded was a huge goal for everyone.  Where traveling from Freeport to Qeynos was a huge journey few had taken.  When Blackburrow was full and everyone begged for sows and mino axes were all the rage.  I truly miss those times, but I guess you can never go back.  Maybe a classic version for gameboy? =P

